"{\"uid\": \"coastaldigest.com-news-top-story-mangaluru-athletes-set-shine-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Mangaluru: Two athletes from Mangaluru are gearing up to represent India at the Paris Olympics starting on July 26.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.291401450889404e-64, \"text\": \"Mangaluru\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\"}, {\"begin\": 31, \"end\": 40, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.291401450889404e-64, \"text\": \"Mangaluru\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\"}, {\"begin\": 69, \"end\": 74, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5205543256178234e-33, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Poovamma MR, a seasoned member of the Indian women's 4x400m relay team, and Mijo Chacko Kurian, selected for the men's 4x400m relay team, are poised to showcase their talent on the international stage.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 156, \"end\": 168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_in_India\", \"score\": 0.9999999994670361, \"rank\": 5.326034326727458e-10, \"text\": \"Indian women\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_in_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_in_India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Poovamma MR had a notable moment recently, marking her third interaction with Prime Minister Narendra Modi.\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on her journey, she shared with the Prime Minister that she was just 18 when she served as a reserve member for the 2008 Olympics and was part of the team again in 2016.\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Determined to break a longstanding barrier, she mentioned that the team had not reached the finals since 2002, but this time, they aim to create a national record and secure a spot in the finals.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Prime Minister commended her confidence and dedication.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This was my third interaction with the PM.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I met him in 2014 and 2018.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier, we showed him our medals, and he congratulated us.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, he asked us questions about our experiences and aspirations.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It felt wonderful,\\\" Poovamma remarked.\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Currently training in Patiala, she is set to depart for a 20-day training camp in Poland before heading to Paris.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patiala\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.451272293539288e-28, \"text\": \"Patiala\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patiala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patiala\"}, {\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.9992383515818308, \"rank\": 0.0007618806061752825, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}, {\"begin\": 1218, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998626663, \"rank\": 1.377015656137364e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In contrast, Mijo Chacko Kurian is making his Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His journey began in class XII when he switched from cricket to athletics upon seeing runners at the NMPT stadium while Mangala Stadium was under renovation.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1314, \"end\": 1317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twelfth_grade\", \"score\": 0.8069286908641575, \"rank\": 0.16200223272031983, \"text\": \"XII\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twelfth_grade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twelfth_grade\"}, {\"begin\": 1388, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Mangalore_Port\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NMPT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Mangalore_Port\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Mangalore_Port\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Living nearby, he approached the coach and joined the training sessions.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite initial struggles, he balanced his studies in engineering with his growing passion for athletics.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His dedication paid off, leading him to leave college after two-and-a-half years to focus fully on his athletic career.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now a junior warrant officer with the Indian Air Force, Mijo is ready to make his mark in Paris.\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1783, \"end\": 1799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Air_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.57310817125982e-39, \"text\": \"Indian Air Force\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Air_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Air_Force\"}, {\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998626663, \"rank\": 1.377015656137364e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As these athletes prepare for their Olympic journey, their stories of perseverance and dedication inspire many back home, highlighting the vibrant sporting spirit of Mangaluru.\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 2019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2009, \"end\": 2018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.291401450889404e-64, \"text\": \"Mangaluru\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bengaluru, Nov 26: Karnataka is taking its first concrete steps towards lifting a three-decade-old ban on student elections in colleges and universities.\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2042, \"end\": 2051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2643368182658296e-41, \"text\": \"Karnataka\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deputy Chief Minister D.K.\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shivakumar announced Wednesday that the state government will form a small committee to study the reintroduction of campus polls, a practice halted in 1989 following incidents of violence.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2392, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking at a 'Constitution Day' event organised by the Karnataka Congress, Mr. Shivakumar underscored the move's aim: nurturing new political leadership from the grassroots.\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2450, \"end\": 2459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2643368182658296e-41, \"text\": \"Karnataka\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\"}, {\"begin\": 2460, \"end\": 2468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9785109680770505e-44, \"text\": \"Congress\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_National_Congress\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Recently, (Leader of the Opposition in Lok Sabha) Rahul Gandhi wrote a letter to me and Chief Minister (Siddaramaiah) asking us to think about restarting student elections,\\\" Shivakumar stated.\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2610, \"end\": 2619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lok_Sabha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9172754142271875e-23, \"text\": \"Lok Sabha\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lok_Sabha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lok_Sabha\"}, {\"begin\": 2621, \"end\": 2633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rahul_Gandhi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rahul Gandhi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rahul_Gandhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rahul_Gandhi\"}, {\"begin\": 2675, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siddaramaiah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Siddaramaiah\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siddaramaiah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siddaramaiah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am announcing today that we will form a small committee and seek a report on this.\\\"\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Student elections were banned in Karnataka in 1989, largely due to concerns over violence and the infiltration of political party affiliates into campus life.\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2885, \"end\": 2894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2643368182658296e-41, \"text\": \"Karnataka\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ban effectively extinguished vibrant student bodies and the pipeline of young leaders they often produced.\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr. Shivakumar, who also serves as the Karnataka Congress president, said that former student leaders will be consulted to \\\"study the pros and cons\\\" of the re-introduction.\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3162, \"end\": 3171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2643368182658296e-41, \"text\": \"Karnataka\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka\"}, {\"begin\": 3172, \"end\": 3190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_Congress_of_the_Republic_of_Peru\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Congress President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_Congress_of_the_Republic_of_Peru\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_Congress_of_the_Republic_of_Peru\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Acknowledging the history of the ban, he added, \\\"There were many criminal activities taking place back then.\", \"from\": 3297, \"to\": 3405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will see how we can conduct (student) elections by regulating such criminal activities.\\\"\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Deputy CM reminisced about his own journey, which began on campus.\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3510, \"end\": 3512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_minister\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1143794794728788e-51, \"text\": \"CM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_minister\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_minister\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He recalled his political activism at Sri Jagadguru Renukacharya College leading to his first Assembly ticket in 1985 at the age of 23.\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3608, \"end\": 3611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shri\", \"score\": 0.9999922359112497, \"rank\": 7.764148759195338e-06, \"text\": \"Sri\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shri\"}, {\"begin\": 3612, \"end\": 3621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jagadguru\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jagadguru\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jagadguru\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jagadguru\"}, {\"begin\": 3622, \"end\": 3634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renukacharya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Renukacharya\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renukacharya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renukacharya\"}, {\"begin\": 3664, \"end\": 3672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland_Assembly\", \"score\": 0.9876894536651943, \"rank\": 0.012458388906401188, \"text\": \"Assembly\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland_Assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland_Assembly\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's how student leadership was at the time.\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3753, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Such leadership has gone today.\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3785, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"College elections have stopped,\\\" he lamented, adding that for many, college elections were \\\"like a big movement\\\" where leaders were forged.\", \"from\": 3786, \"to\": 3925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The move, driven by the Congress high command's push to cultivate young talent, will face scrutiny from academics and university authorities who have, in the past, expressed concern that the return of polls could disrupt the peaceful academic environment and turn campuses into political battlegrounds.\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 4229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3951, \"end\": 3972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_Working_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Congress high command\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_Working_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_Working_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mangaluru, Nov 30: A 22-year-old college student succumbed to her injuries at a private hospital in Mangaluru today, days after she was hit by a goods tempo while crossing a road in Padubidri.\", \"from\": 4237, \"to\": 4429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4337, \"end\": 4346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.291401450889404e-64, \"text\": \"Mangaluru\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\"}, {\"begin\": 4419, \"end\": 4428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padubidri\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Padubidri\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padubidri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padubidri\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The deceased has been identified as Preksha, a resident of Nadsalu Billitota in Padubidri.\", \"from\": 4431, \"to\": 4521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4511, \"end\": 4520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padubidri\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Padubidri\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padubidri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Padubidri\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fatal incident occurred as Preksha, who was returning home after completing her examination, attempted to cross the service road towards Mangaluru.\", \"from\": 4522, \"to\": 4673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4663, \"end\": 4672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.291401450889404e-64, \"text\": \"Mangaluru\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was struck by a goods tempo approaching from the Udupi side, causing her to fall and sustain a severe head injury.\", \"from\": 4674, \"to\": 4792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4727, \"end\": 4732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Udupi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.26790555069154e-23, \"text\": \"Udupi\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Udupi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Udupi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prompt action from local residents ensured she received immediate first aid before being rushed to a hospital in Mangaluru for specialised treatment.\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 4943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4907, \"end\": 4916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.291401450889404e-64, \"text\": \"Mangaluru\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite medical efforts, she passed away while undergoing care.\", \"from\": 4944, \"to\": 5007, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Preksha was a student at Karavali College, Vamanjoor on the outskirts of Mangaluru city.\", \"from\": 5009, \"to\": 5097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5034, \"end\": 5042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karavali\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karavali\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karavali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karavali\"}, {\"begin\": 5082, \"end\": 5091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.291401450889404e-64, \"text\": \"Mangaluru\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tragedy is compounded by the fact that she belonged to a financially vulnerable family, having previously lost her father.\", \"from\": 5098, \"to\": 5224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is survived by her mother and brother.\", \"from\": 5225, \"to\": 5267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A case related to the accident has been registered at the Padubidri police station, and an investigation is underway to determine the exact circumstances that led to the collision.\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The incident highlights the growing concerns over road safety, particularly on busy service roads, and serves as a tragic reminder of the human cost of traffic accidents.\", \"from\": 5450, \"to\": 5620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mangaluru, Nov 29: Around 12,500 healthcare students from Medical, Dental, AYUSH, Pharmacy, Nursing, Physiotherapy and Allied Health Sciences colleges of Dakshina Kannada, affiliated to Rajiv Gandhi University of Health Sciences (RGUHS), took part in a massive walkathon to promote awareness on Organ Donation and Nasha Mukth Bharat.\", \"from\": 5624, \"to\": 5957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5624, \"end\": 5633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.291401450889404e-64, \"text\": \"Mangaluru\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mangalore\"}, {\"begin\": 5725, \"end\": 5738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_therapy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Physiotherapy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_therapy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Physical_therapy\"}, {\"begin\": 5743, \"end\": 5749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allies_of_World_War_II\", \"score\": 0.9990322933395894, \"rank\": 0.0007624571997465757, \"text\": \"Allied\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allies_of_World_War_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allies_of_World_War_II\"}, {\"begin\": 5778, \"end\": 5794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dakshina_Kannada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6205831828685513e-88, \"text\": \"Dakshina Kannada\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dakshina_Kannada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dakshina_Kannada\"}, {\"begin\": 5919, \"end\": 5933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Organ_donation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Organ Donation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Organ_donation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Organ_donation\"}, {\"begin\": 5938, \"end\": 5943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasha_(film)\", \"score\": 0.9505966332579697, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nasha\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasha_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasha_(film)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The inaugural ceremony was held at Mangala Stadium.\", \"from\": 5959, \"to\": 6010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Bhagavan B C, Hon'ble Vice-Chancellor of RGUHS, delivered the welcome address.\", \"from\": 6011, \"to\": 6092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6014, \"end\": 6022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bhagavan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The walkathon was flagged off by Shri U T Khader, Hon'ble Speaker of the Karnataka Legislative Assembly, and presided over by Shri Dinesh Gundu Rao, Hon'ble Minister for Health, Family Welfare and Dakshina Kannada District In-charge.\", \"from\": 6093, \"to\": 6326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6166, \"end\": 6196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka_Legislative_Assembly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8046340408272216e-64, \"text\": \"Karnataka Legislative Assembly\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka_Legislative_Assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karnataka_Legislative_Assembly\"}, {\"begin\": 6224, \"end\": 6240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dinesh_Gundu_Rao\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dinesh Gundu Rao\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dinesh_Gundu_Rao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dinesh_Gundu_Rao\"}, {\"begin\": 6290, \"end\": 6306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour